**************************************
Birdy Bot Critter Camera and Webserver
**************************************

birdyBot.py: (Python) monitors a PIR sensor and snaps pictures
when it senses motion.

pictureServer.js: (node) a webserver used to view the snapshots

To run the birdyBot script: sudo python birdybot.py &
To run the webserver: node pictureserver.js &


